ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course will only be taught as such this year, but was there ever a chance for a similar seminar on Modernism and the Project of Modernity to be offered in the future, I would encourage every student with a rigorous interest in the period and the time's literature to take it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It really helped me broaden my understanding of the period's literature and trace connections with the discourse on modernity in my discipline.

This course has been great for the manner in which it's allowed me some breathing room to pursue my own interests independently while itself being general enough for me to explore some of the broad conceptual frameworks that might pertain to this work.
